title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Among the titles listed by Pocket Books as out of print as of 9/20/84 in Publishers Weekly, June 22, 1984, p. 114, is Words Most Often Misspelled & Misspronounced.
